<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Searching for Soulfire...</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Arkhon">Arkhon</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 4:32 p.m. 12/4/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Searching for Soulfire...<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Starting with a strange message mentioning Zimel's Blades, i end up looking for an old friend of a dwarf called Groflah Steadirt. When i ask that dwarf about this old friend of his, he tells me that he won't talk about it there.

<P>So i wait, expecting him to leave his house any moment, which he eventually does, but in a way i didn't expect: he just disapeared. I guess it means he moved to another of the Freeport's zones. The thing is, he only left for a few mins (maybe 10). I need to find him back with the hope he will tell me more at this new location he goes.
<P>Does anyone know where he is? 10 mins to look for him every EQ day (40 mins) is really tedious. Waiting all that time to search a few houses is killing me.
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
